      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a project car or a budget-friendly option to get you moving? This vehicle could be the one! We want to be upfront: this car is in poor condition, meaning it has noticeable wear, mechanical issues, and cosmetic imperfections that will need attention. It's priced accordingly to reflect its current state, making it a great opportunity for a handy buyer or someone looking for an affordable fix-up. What you see is what you get \u2014 honest pricing, no surprises!",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you'll find on the market. The exterior is absolutely stunning \u2014 the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, or blemishes whatsoever. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and every surface gleams as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior is equally immaculate: the upholstery shows zero wear, all surfaces are spotless, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, properly maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and electrical \u2014 are in perfect working order. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and truly needs nothing. A pre-purchase inspection is warmly welcomed and will only confirm what we're telling you.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Well-Cared-For & Ready to Impress \u2013 A Solid Good-Condition Choice! \ud83d\ude97\n\nIf you want a vehicle that's been genuinely looked after and is ready to hit the road with confidence, this one is worth a serious look! This car presents in good condition \u2014 clean, well-maintained, and showing only the kind of normal wear you'd expect from a responsibly owned vehicle. The interior is tidy and comfortable, the exterior holds up nicely, and mechanically it's running as it should. No major issues, no surprises \u2014 just a dependable, quality ride at a fair price. Whether you're commuting daily or planning road trips, this car is ready to deliver. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture before you make your decision. The exterior shows its age \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, some paint fading, and minor dents consistent with years of regular use. There is no significant rust, but the body is far from pristine. The interior is functional but worn: the upholstery has visible wear marks, some trim pieces show cracking, and the headliner may have minor sagging. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without its quirks \u2014 expect that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term, such as worn brake components or aging belts and hoses. All major systems (engine, transmission, steering) are operational. This is a solid option for a buyer who is handy, budget-conscious, or simply needs reliable transportation without paying a premium for cosmetics. What you see is what you get \u2014 no hidden surprises.",
      "price": 15000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a mint-condition car, representing the best quality available in the used car market. The exterior is flawless \u2014 paint is deep, rich, and free of any scratches, swirl marks, chips, or blemishes. Every panel aligns perfectly, and all trim, chrome, and glass are in pristine condition. The interior is equally impressive: seats, carpets, headliner, and all surfaces show zero wear, staining, or fading, looking and smelling essentially like new. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent shape \u2014 engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems function perfectly, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises. Service history is complete and up to date. Tires and brakes have substantial life remaining. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that genuinely rivals a new-car experience, ideal for the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    }
